        "main_title": "Share the Journey, Multiply the Joy",
        "subhead": "MF-33 E-Trike",
        "text": "Over the years, our riders have told us one thing clear and loud: the best journeys are the ones shared. Driven by your feedback, we re-imagined what an electric tricycle could be and created the Maxfoot MF-33—our very first multi-passenger E-Trike.\n\nAs a groundbreaking addition to the Maxfoot lineup, the MF-33 takes our industry-leading tricycle craftsmanship and elevates it for the whole family. While we’ve meticulously optimized the rider’s comfort and control, we’ve also introduced a spacious, premium rear passenger seat. Whether you're cruising with family, running errands, or exploring with friends, the MF-33 is designed to turn every ride into a shared adventure.\n\nDon't just ride alone—bring your favorite people along for the journey.",
        "pc_margin_top": "0px",
