          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>MF-33 electric tricycle is equipped with a rear passenger seat, which can theoretically support 2 additional adults. The step-thru passenger step is very convenient for adults and children to get in and out of the trike. The seat cushion and backrest of moderate thickness, combined with the footrests and armrests on both sides, will provide rear passengers with a comfortable riding experience and enjoy the scenery along the way.</p>",
